  "projects": [
    {
      "title": "Tuto Figma",
      "context": [
        "During my first-year internship at the Ecole Nationale Supérieure de Cognitique, I was responsible for supervising second-grade students, who were themselves on an internship, in order to introduce them to the school and its fields of study. One of the activities I organized was to make them understand what Figma is and introduce them to its principles. It was a really enriching experience in terms of pedagogy.",
        "I also prepared a tutorial to explore all the main features of Figma.  Then, to let their creativity speak, we offered them to model a music listening app, and given the enthusiasm and investment that students had, it was really worth being fully invested in this activity and internship, I am still very grateful to them! "
      ],
      "created": "2024-06-26",
      "duration": "1",
      "projectDuty": ["UX/UI Design"],
