    {
      "title": "DeskFriend",
      "context": [
        "In my school, I had the opportunity to explore the key phases of user-centered design through a concrete project: analysis, mock-up and user tests. At the beginning, each group received a problem to solve and then with each phase change we passed our project to another group.",
        "The design phase was implemented through the DeskFriend project. It was a particularly important step for me, because this is the area that interests me most in this school. ",
        "That's why, in our team of 4 people, I was fully responsible for the technical part of the design mockup — in other words, I was the one who put into practice the ideas we had thought about together. I have implemented a component-based approach to enhance visual consistency and facilitate edits. I also designed an intuitive and efficient prototype, while providing the artistic direction and technical management on Figma, to ensure a smooth and easily adaptable user experience."
      ],
      "created": "2025-02-13",
      "duration": "1",
      "projectDuty": ["UX/UI Design"],
