    {
      "title": "Krystal",
      "context": [
        "The Krystal is THE sports tournament organized by the AS de Bordeaux INP for the 7 engineering schools of Bordeaux INP and the preparation of the INP.",
        "A friend who was in charge of the event offered me to make the logos, I accepted without hesitation! The project was super fun to do! For this KRYSTAL, they decided to assign film themes to each school. So it was necessary to adapt each logo to its respective film, which took more work but was the most fun part of the project in the end! ",
        "I cannot express how grateful I am to them for giving me the opportunity to participate in such a significant project. I owe them a whole lot!"
